Comment: 0,0:00:01.54,0:00:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,845年 因突然出現的超大型巨人
Comment: 0,0:00:06.75,0:00:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,以及盔甲巨人
Comment: 0,0:00:09.24,0:00:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,所有的日常 隨著城牆的破壞一同破滅
Comment: 0,0:00:14.67,0:00:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,人類放棄瑪利亞之牆
Comment: 0,0:00:17.93,0:00:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,失去了兩成的人口以及三分之一的領土
Comment: 0,0:00:21.60,0:00:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,活動領域退後至羅塞之牆
Comment: 0,0:00:27.02,0:00:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,然後...
Comment: 0,0:00:28.52,0:00:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,850年
Comment: 0,0:00:30.98,0:00:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,人類的反擊...
Comment: 0,0:00:33.31,0:00:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,從現在開始!
Comment: 0,0:00:37.26,0:00:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,目標在眼前 超大型巨人
Comment: 0,0:00:40.95,0:00:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這是個機會
Comment: 0,0:00:42.28,0:00:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,絕對不要放過
Comment: 0,0:00:46.76,0:00:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,唷!
Comment: 0,0:00:49.07,0:00:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,五年沒見了呢
Comment: 0,0:00:50.32,0:00:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,OP
Comment: 0,0:02:50.17,0:02:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這傢伙...
Comment: 0,0:02:51.57,0:02:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,居然以固定砲為目標
Comment: 0,0:02:54.82,0:02:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,看來針對開關門也不是偶然
Comment: 0,0:02:58.61,0:03:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,果然這傢伙有...
Comment: 0,0:03:01.73,0:03:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,智慧
Comment: 0,0:03:08.29,0:03:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但是這是個機會
Comment: 0,0:03:10.93,0:03:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,能破壞城牆的只有他
Comment: 0,0:03:15.37,0:03:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,只要能夠收拾掉他
Comment: 0,0:03:24.86,0:03:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,太弱了
Comment: 0,0:03:28.42,0:03:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,到手啦!
Comment: 0,0:03:33.70,0:03:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,好... 好熱!
Comment: 0,0:03:42.85,0:03:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,上啊!!
Comment: 0,0:03:50.20,0:03:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,打偏了?
Comment: 0,0:03:57.17,0:03:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不...
Comment: 0,0:03:58.89,0:04:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,超大型巨人消失了
Comment: 0,0:04:03.46,0:04:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連 是你打敗的嗎?
Comment: 0,0:04:06.42,0:04:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不對
Comment: 0,0:04:08.40,0:04:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,跟五年前一樣
Comment: 0,0:04:10.40,0:04:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那傢伙突然出現
Comment: 0,0:04:12.24,0:04:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,又突然消失掉
Comment: 0,0:04:16.84,0:04:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,抱歉
Comment: 0,0:04:17.78,0:04:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我讓他跑了
Comment: 0,0:04:18.87,0:04:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你在抱歉什麼 我們根本無法動彈呢
Comment: 0,0:04:21.79,0:04:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,喂 是說這個的時候嗎?
Comment: 0,0:04:24.42,0:04:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,城牆已經被破壞掉了
Comment: 0,0:04:26.34,0:04:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不快點補起來的話 巨人可又要進來了
Comment: 0,0:04:29.87,0:04:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你們在幹嘛?
Comment: 0,0:04:31.39,0:04:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,超大型巨人出現 即視同作戰
Comment: 0,0:04:35.23,0:04:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,立刻回到本部
Comment: 0,0:04:36.97,0:04:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,有和他接觸過的 記得向本部回報
Comment: 0,0:04:39.76,0:04:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是!
Comment: 0,0:04:40.47,0:04:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,期待先遣部隊的好表現
Comment: 0,0:04:59.30,0:05:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,請將帶走的財物縮小在最小範圍內
Comment: 0,0:05:01.50,0:05:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,冷靜地前往避難
Comment: 0,0:05:07.46,0:05:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這裡被突破的話
Comment: 0,0:05:09.29,0:05:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,五年前的慘劇又將再次上演
Comment: 0,0:05:13.35,0:05:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我們要在這裡阻止巨人們前進
Comment: 0,0:05:18.86,0:05:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,迎擊準備
Comment: 0,0:05:22.76,0:05:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,開砲!
Comment: 0,0:05:30.56,0:05:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,上啊!
Comment: 0,0:05:35.56,0:05:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你們這些訓練兵
Comment: 0,0:05:37.29,0:05:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,也是通過了畢業演習的優秀士兵
Comment: 0,0:05:40.49,0:05:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,期待你們在這次作戰中的表現
Comment: 0,0:05:44.01,0:05:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,沒事的 漢娜
Comment: 0,0:05:46.38,0:05:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我一定會保護妳的
Comment: 0,0:05:48.42,0:05:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,法蘭茲...
Comment: 0,0:05:53.26,0:05:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,沒事吧 阿爾敏
Comment: 0,0:05:56.61,0:05:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,沒事的
Comment: 0,0:05:57.86,0:06:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這毛病很快就會停止
Comment: 0,0:06:00.59,0:06:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但是 現在情況不太妙
Comment: 0,0:06:02.28,0:06:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就現況而言 我們沒有將8公尺寬的大洞
Comment: 0,0:06:04.86,0:06:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,馬上填補起來的技術
Comment: 0,0:06:07.41,0:06:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,前門附近的那塊岩石也是 到最後還是無法搬回去
Comment: 0,0:06:13.74,0:06:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,在無法修補大洞的這點上 這座城市將會被遺棄
Comment: 0,0:06:21.97,0:06:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,羅塞之牆被突破
Comment: 0,0:06:24.06,0:06:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,也只是時間上的問題
Comment: 0,0:06:26.37,0:06:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,況且只要他們有心
Comment: 0,0:06:29.64,0:06:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,無論何時都能夠將人類趕盡殺絕
Comment: 0,0:06:32.30,0:06:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,阿爾敏
Comment: 0,0:06:34.05,0:06:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,冷靜點!
Comment: 0,0:06:35.50,0:06:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,現在和當時不同
Comment: 0,0:06:37.23,0:06:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,人類已經不會...
Comment: 0,0:06:38.71,0:06:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,再輸給巨人了!
Comment: 0,0:06:45.18,0:06:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,抱歉...
Comment: 0,0:06:47.30,0:06:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,沒事了
Comment: 0,0:07:04.24,0:07:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,喂 你有在認真下嗎?
Comment: 0,0:07:08.55,0:07:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你看 又是我贏了
Comment: 0,0:07:13.09,0:07:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,明明每個月都跟我下一次
Comment: 0,0:07:16.94,0:07:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你還是沒進步呢
Comment: 0,0:07:19.41,0:07:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,皮克希斯
Comment: 0,0:07:20.76,0:07:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不 不
Comment: 0,0:07:22.03,0:07:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我還不夠格贏巴爾托公爵
Comment: 0,0:07:29.51,0:07:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你不是負責南方司令的最高權力者嗎?
Comment: 0,0:07:37.51,0:07:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,以這種程度的技術跟頭腦 是想要怎樣贏巨人呢?
Comment: 0,0:07:42.08,0:07:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,皮克希斯司令
Comment: 0,0:07:43.85,0:07:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,有傳令
Comment: 0,0:07:45.37,0:07:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你想幹嘛? 無禮的...
Comment: 0,0:07:47.27,0:07:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,托洛斯特區出現了超大型巨人
Comment: 0,0:07:50.35,0:07:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,開關門被破壞了
Comment: 0,0:08:06.22,0:08:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這真是好喝的酒
Comment: 0,0:08:08.82,0:08:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,作為戰場上的朋友 我就虛心收下了
Comment: 0,0:08:14.17,0:08:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,喂
Comment: 0,0:08:15.57,0:08:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,等等 皮克希斯
Comment: 0,0:08:18.77,0:08:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,皮克希斯
Comment: 0,0:08:20.07,0:08:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,給我等等
Comment: 0,0:08:21.81,0:08:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我可不允許你離開這裡
Comment: 0,0:08:24.97,0:08:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,立刻給我召集士兵
Comment: 0,0:08:26.93,0:08:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,保衛我的領地
Comment: 0,0:08:30.09,0:08:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這才是你的職務吧
Comment: 0,0:08:35.36,0:08:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,巴爾托公爵
Comment: 0,0:08:36.96,0:08:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,現在托洛斯特區的士兵們可是拼上性命在戰鬥唷
Comment: 0,0:08:41.95,0:08:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,司令 我去準備馬
Comment: 0,0:08:45.29,0:08:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,然後我想恐怕會有很多人失去性命
Comment: 0,0:08:49.42,0:08:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,而現在我在說話的這一刻也是
Comment: 0,0:08:53.40,0:08:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,反正也是些廉價的生命
Comment: 0,0:08:55.14,0:08:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,捨棄掉就好
Comment: 0,0:08:57.04,0:09:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,況且在棋盤上一直輸給我的你 去了狀況也不會有所改變
Comment: 0,0:09:04.23,0:09:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,請您安心 公爵
Comment: 0,0:09:07.01,0:09:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,在實戰上面對巨人的話
Comment: 0,0:09:09.65,0:09:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,沒有司令親自出手的必要
Comment: 0,0:09:15.31,0:09:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,別說了
Comment: 0,0:09:17.87,0:09:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,巴爾托公爵
Comment: 0,0:09:19.50,0:09:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就請您一如往常地度過安穩的一天
Comment: 0,0:09:26.87,0:09:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,喂...
Comment: 0,0:09:29.13,0:09:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,皮克希斯
Comment: 0,0:09:30.58,0:09:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,給我回來 皮克希斯
Comment: 0,0:09:33.41,0:09:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,皮克希斯!
Comment: 0,0:09:24.95,0:09:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,CM
Comment: 0,0:09:48.13,0:09:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那麼就照平時訓練一樣分成各班
Comment: 0,0:09:50.81,0:09:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,在駐紮軍團的指揮下
Comment: 0,0:09:53.01,0:09:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,進行補給支援 情報傳遞
Comment: 0,0:09:55.26,0:09:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,以及討伐巨人等任務
Comment: 0,0:09:58.35,0:10:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,前衛部由駐紮軍團負責
Comment: 0,0:10:01.36,0:10:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,中衛部由我們率領的訓練兵團負責
Comment: 0,0:10:04.40,0:10:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,而後衛部則以駐紮軍團的精銳部隊負責
Comment: 0,0:10:08.40,0:10:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,依照報告前衛部已經全滅了
Comment: 0,0:10:13.54,0:10:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,外圍的那群廢物
Comment: 0,0:10:15.15,0:10:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,允許了巨人的進攻
Comment: 0,0:10:17.73,0:10:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,也就是說
Comment: 0,0:10:18.82,0:10:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,現在處於的狀況 就算後門遭盔甲巨人破壞也不足為奇
Comment: 0,0:10:26.53,0:10:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,怎麼會...
Comment: 0,0:10:27.62,0:10:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,騙人的吧
Comment: 0,0:10:29.32,0:10:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,羅塞之牆也被破壞掉的話...
Comment: 0,0:10:31.95,0:10:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,正式聽令
Comment: 0,0:10:34.05,0:10:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,現在是前衛部的迎擊期
Comment: 0,0:10:36.93,0:10:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這次作戰的目的只有一個
Comment: 0,0:10:39.35,0:10:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,在居民避難完成以前死守羅塞之牆
Comment: 0,0:10:44.53,0:10:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,然後 我想你們知道的 陣前逃亡將處以死刑
Comment: 0,0:10:49.74,0:10:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,大家準備好獻上自己的心臟!
Comment: 0,0:10:52.22,0:10:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,解散!
Comment: 0,0:10:53.48,0:10:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是!!
Comment: 0,0:11:00.15,0:11:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,為什麼是今天...
Comment: 0,0:11:02.30,0:11:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,明明我明天就能夠到內地去了
Comment: 0,0:11:07.37,0:11:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,沒事吧?
Comment: 0,0:11:14.35,0:11:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不要... 不要... 不要... 不要...
Comment: 0,0:11:24.42,0:11:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,礙眼!
Comment: 0,0:11:26.15,0:11:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,喂 約翰...
Comment: 0,0:11:27.39,0:11:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你怎麼了?
Comment: 0,0:11:28.37,0:11:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你說我怎麼了?
Comment: 0,0:11:30.08,0:11:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,別給我說得這麼悠哉 你這趕著去投胎的傢伙!
Comment: 0,0:11:33.48,0:11:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你是因為自願進入調查軍團 所以早已有送死的覺悟
Comment: 0,0:11:39.89,0:11:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我可是明天開始就要去內地的啊
Comment: 0,0:11:42.21,0:11:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,冷靜點!
Comment: 0,0:11:43.01,0:11:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,冷靜點等死是嗎!?
Comment: 0,0:11:44.99,0:11:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不對 你給我想起來
Comment: 0,0:11:48.08,0:11:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我們在訓練兵團的這三年
Comment: 0,0:11:52.21,0:11:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這三年我們有好幾次都差點死了
Comment: 0,0:11:55.91,0:11:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,也有真的死掉的人
Comment: 0,0:11:58.06,0:12:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,退出的人跟被趕走的人也是
Comment: 0,0:12:01.38,0:12:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但是我們活了下來
Comment: 0,0:12:03.47,0:12:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,沒錯吧!
Comment: 0,0:12:04.91,0:12:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就算是今天我們也能夠活下去!
Comment: 0,0:12:09.32,0:12:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,今天活下去
Comment: 0,0:12:11.41,0:12:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,明天不就能去內地了?
Comment: 0,0:12:18.70,0:12:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,該死的
Comment: 0,0:12:21.78,0:12:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,走啦 達茲
Comment: 0,0:12:23.55,0:12:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不要給我一直哭
Comment: 0,0:12:27.39,0:12:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連
Comment: 0,0:12:29.42,0:12:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,一旦戰鬥陷入混亂
Comment: 0,0:12:31.07,0:12:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你就來我身邊
Comment: 0,0:12:32.42,0:12:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,蛤?
Comment: 0,0:12:33.52,0:12:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我跟妳是不同小組的吧?
Comment: 0,0:12:35.90,0:12:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,在混亂之下 就無法如想像般地順利
Comment: 0,0:12:39.38,0:12:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,由我來保護你
Comment: 0,0:12:40.94,0:12:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你在說什...
Comment: 0,0:12:42.13,0:12:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,阿卡曼訓練兵
Comment: 0,0:12:44.45,0:12:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,特別准許妳隸屬後衛部隊
Comment: 0,0:12:46.53,0:12:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,給我跟上來
Comment: 0,0:12:47.41,0:12:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,等... 以我的程度只會拖累大家
Comment: 0,0:12:51.51,0:12:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我不是在問妳的判斷
Comment: 0,0:12:54.41,0:12:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,如今才避難已經晚了
Comment: 0,0:12:56.26,0:12:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,居民的附近需要更多的精銳保護
Comment: 0,0:12:59.37,0:13:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,可是...
Comment: 0,0:13:00.33,0:13:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,喂!
Comment: 0,0:13:02.10,0:13:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,給我適可而止一點 米卡莎
Comment: 0,0:13:04.33,0:13:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不要連妳都給我亂
Comment: 0,0:13:06.85,0:13:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,現在可是人類滅亡的危機
Comment: 0,0:13:09.14,0:13:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,妳在那邊堅持自己的判斷是怎樣
Comment: 0,0:13:16.25,0:13:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,抱歉
Comment: 0,0:13:17.84,0:13:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我不夠冷靜
Comment: 0,0:13:22.10,0:13:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我只有一個請求
Comment: 0,0:13:27.87,0:13:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,請你不要死
Comment: 0,0:13:37.35,0:13:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我不會死的
Comment: 0,0:13:38.89,0:13:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我怎麼可以...
Comment: 0,0:13:40.78,0:13:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,在這邊就死掉呢
Comment: 0,0:13:45.71,0:13:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,因為我還不了解這個世界的真實姿態
Comment: 0,0:13:53.46,0:13:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,遺留下來的歷史文獻裡並沒有紀錄巨人出現的原因
Comment: 0,0:13:58.97,0:14:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,幾乎是完全不明的
Comment: 0,0:14:01.75,0:14:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,現在已經清楚的巨人生態
Comment: 0,0:14:05.10,0:14:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是來自於調查軍團的最新報告書
Comment: 0,0:14:09.09,0:14:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,無法確認巨人具備像人類般的智慧
Comment: 0,0:14:13.13,0:14:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,因此不曾有過跟我們溝通的例子
Comment: 0,0:14:18.80,0:14:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,巨人身體的構造跟其他生物有著根本上的不同
Comment: 0,0:14:23.89,0:14:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,完全沒有生殖器官
Comment: 0,0:14:25.66,0:14:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,繁殖方式也是不明
Comment: 0,0:14:28.34,0:14:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但幾乎都是男性的體格
Comment: 0,0:14:31.79,0:14:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,他們的身體具有極高的溫度
Comment: 0,0:14:34.66,0:14:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,而且最難以理解的是
Comment: 0,0:14:36.11,0:14:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,對人類以外的生物完全不感興趣
Comment: 0,0:14:41.07,0:14:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,巨人唯一行動原理就是吃人
Comment: 0,0:14:44.95,0:14:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但從巨人能在無人類的環境下存活百年以上這點來想
Comment: 0,0:14:51.46,0:14:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,能夠推測出進食這點並非必要
Comment: 0,0:14:56.48,0:14:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,也就是說
Comment: 0,0:14:57.58,0:14:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,目的不在於捕食
Comment: 0,0:14:59.64,0:15:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,而是進行殺戮
Comment: 0,0:15:03.76,0:15:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,然後
Comment: 0,0:15:04.70,0:15:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,將人類逼到如此絕境的最大原因是...
Comment: 0,0:15:08.62,0:15:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,巨人令人驚訝的生命力
Comment: 0,0:15:12.42,0:15:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,以前的人類雖然擁有大砲技術
Comment: 0,0:15:15.85,0:15:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不過光是這樣 還是無法與之抗衡
Comment: 0,0:15:18.85,0:15:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,巨人即使頭被打飛也不會死
Comment: 0,0:15:22.10,0:15:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,雖然個體會有差異
Comment: 0,0:15:24.19,0:15:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但是失去的頭部會在一到兩分鐘內恢復原狀
Comment: 0,0:15:27.98,0:15:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,怎麼會...
Comment: 0,0:15:29.37,0:15:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,明明光是大隻就很難應付了
Comment: 0,0:15:31.41,0:15:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,教官 那麼巨人是不死之身嗎?
Comment: 0,0:15:35.89,0:15:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,並不是不死之身
Comment: 0,0:15:37.93,0:15:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,打倒巨人的方法只有一個
Comment: 0,0:15:41.12,0:15:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,朝這裡下手
Comment: 0,0:15:43.35,0:15:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,巨人一旦這個部位受到嚴重的損傷
Comment: 0,0:15:46.27,0:15:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就會因無法再生而死亡
Comment: 0,0:15:49.43,0:15:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,因此為了切下較硬的肉塊
Comment: 0,0:15:51.49,0:15:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就要使用這兩把刀
Comment: 0,0:15:54.27,0:15:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,只要攻擊能夠擊中巨人的要害
Comment: 0,0:15:57.44,0:16:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就能夠在不令其再生的情況下即刻死亡
Comment: 0,0:16:09.69,0:16:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我說 阿爾敏
Comment: 0,0:16:11.56,0:16:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你不覺得這是個好機會嗎?
Comment: 0,0:16:15.17,0:16:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,在進入調查軍團之前
Comment: 0,0:16:17.88,0:16:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,如果能在首場戰役有所表現
Comment: 0,0:16:20.08,0:16:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,身為新兵的我們
Comment: 0,0:16:21.83,0:16:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,勢必能夠快速晉升
Comment: 0,0:16:31.05,0:16:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是啊... 沒錯
Comment: 0,0:16:33.93,0:16:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我先告訴你們兩個
Comment: 0,0:16:35.55,0:16:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這次自願加入調查軍團的人可多了
Comment: 0,0:16:39.02,0:16:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,剛才雖然被艾連搶先一步
Comment: 0,0:16:41.60,0:16:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不過這次我可不會輸
Comment: 0,0:16:43.04,0:16:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你說的唷 托瑪斯
Comment: 0,0:16:45.04,0:16:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,來比比看誰可以獵到最多隻巨人吧
Comment: 0,0:16:48.22,0:16:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你可別在數量上作弊喔
Comment: 0,0:16:49.61,0:16:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,第三十四班 推進!
Comment: 0,0:16:51.49,0:16:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,前去支援前衛部隊
Comment: 0,0:16:54.45,0:16:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,好!
Comment: 0,0:16:55.20,0:16:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,走吧!!
Comment: 0,0:16:56.04,0:16:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,喔!!
Comment: 0,0:17:20.22,0:17:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,已經有那麼多巨人...
Comment: 0,0:17:22.29,0:17:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,前衛部隊根本全滅了
Comment: 0,0:17:24.80,0:17:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,在搞三小啊 那些平時作威作福的前輩們
Comment: 0,0:17:28.88,0:17:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,絕對不是我太過樂觀
Comment: 0,0:17:31.73,0:17:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這實在是...
Comment: 0,0:17:34.37,0:17:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是奇行種!
Comment: 0,0:17:36.31,0:17:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,快閃開!!
Comment: 0,0:17:54.69,0:17:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,奇怪...?
Comment: 0,0:18:20.66,0:18:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你在幹什麼!
Comment: 0,0:18:23.06,0:18:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連!
Comment: 0,0:18:23.84,0:18:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,住手 別單獨行動!
Comment: 0,0:18:29.05,0:18:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,給我站住!!
Comment: 0,0:18:31.95,0:18:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你竟敢把托瑪斯...
Comment: 0,0:18:34.24,0:18:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我絕對...
Comment: 0,0:18:35.81,0:18:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,絕對不會讓你逃走!!
Comment: 0,0:18:48.66,0:18:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連!
Comment: 0,0:18:50.17,0:18:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連
Comment: 0,0:19:07.74,0:19:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,住手... 住手啊...
Comment: 0,0:19:17.31,0:19:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,為什麼... 我...
Comment: 0,0:19:20.64,0:19:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,會這樣看著夥伴們被吃掉的景象...
Comment: 0,0:19:31.69,0:19:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,為什麼... 我的身體...
Comment: 0,0:19:35.25,0:19:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,會無法動彈呢...
Comment: 0,0:19:47.35,0:19:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,阿... 阿爾敏...
Comment: 0,0:19:51.12,0:19:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連
Comment: 0,0:19:52.70,0:19:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連
Comment: 0,0:19:54.32,0:19:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連!
Comment: 0,0:19:57.25,0:19:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,怎麼了? 阿爾敏
Comment: 0,0:19:58.75,0:20:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這本書是爺爺偷藏起來的
Comment: 0,0:20:02.10,0:20:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是描寫外面世界的書
Comment: 0,0:20:05.55,0:20:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你說是描寫外面世界的書?
Comment: 0,0:20:08.10,0:20:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那不是違禁品嗎?
Comment: 0,0:20:10.75,0:20:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,小心被憲兵團抓走喔
Comment: 0,0:20:12.21,0:20:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,現在不是說這個的時候
Comment: 0,0:20:15.09,0:20:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,根據這本書上的記載
Comment: 0,0:20:16.36,0:20:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這個世界上大半都被名為「大海」的水所包圍著呢!
Comment: 0,0:20:20.43,0:20:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,而且「大海」全部都是鹽水
Comment: 0,0:20:23.21,0:20:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你是說鹽?
Comment: 0,0:20:24.84,0:20:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你騙肖
Comment: 0,0:20:26.00,0:20:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,鹽不是很貴重嗎?
Comment: 0,0:20:28.24,0:20:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,商人一定馬上就會搶光了
Comment: 0,0:20:30.81,0:20:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,「大海」寬廣到取之不盡用之不竭
Comment: 0,0:20:33.64,0:20:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,怎麼可...
Comment: 0,0:20:35.88,0:20:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不只是鹽堆得像座山
Comment: 0,0:20:38.59,0:20:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,火焰的水
Comment: 0,0:20:39.98,0:20:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,結冰的大地
Comment: 0,0:20:41.32,0:20:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,砂的冰原
Comment: 0,0:20:43.11,0:20:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,外面的世界一定比這牆內寬廣好幾倍
Comment: 0,0:20:48.07,0:20:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,外面的世界...
Comment: 0,0:20:50.52,0:20:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,然後 這雖然還是秘密...
Comment: 0,0:20:53.97,0:20:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我爸爸跟媽媽說這次要去外面的世界
Comment: 0,0:20:59.05,0:21:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,外面的世界啊
Comment: 0,0:21:01.42,0:21:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,欸 艾連
Comment: 0,0:21:03.35,0:21:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,如果哪天我們可以到外面的世界探險就好了
Comment: 0,0:21:27.04,0:21:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連!
Comment: 0,0:21:29.45,0:21:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我怎麼可以..死在這裡...
Comment: 0,0:21:36.99,0:21:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,阿爾敏
Comment: 0,0:21:39.50,0:21:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是你...
Comment: 0,0:21:41.02,0:21:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,告訴我的
Comment: 0,0:21:44.03,0:21:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,所以我才...
Comment: 0,0:21:46.09,0:21:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,想到外面的...
Comment: 0,0:21:47.83,0:21:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,世界去...
Comment: 0,0:21:52.12,0:21:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連! 快...
Comment: 0,0:21:43.90,0:21:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,NEXT
Comment: 0,0:23:53.76,0:23:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,突然下起的雨
Comment: 0,0:23:56.07,0:23:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那安靜的雨聲
Comment: 0,0:23:58.16,0:23:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,潮濕的空氣
Comment: 0,0:24:00.58,0:24:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,微弱的雨之甜味
Comment: 0,0:24:03.09,0:24:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,讓米卡莎想起過去那悽慘的事件
