Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.54,0:00:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}845年 因突然出現的超大型巨人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.75,0:00:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}以及盔甲巨人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.24,0:00:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}所有的日常 隨著城牆的破壞一同破滅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.67,0:00:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}人類放棄瑪利亞之牆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.93,0:00:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}失去了兩成的人口以及三分之一的領土
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.60,0:00:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}活動領域退後至羅塞之牆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.02,0:00:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}然後...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.52,0:00:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}850年
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.98,0:00:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}人類的反擊...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.31,0:00:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}從現在開始!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.26,0:00:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}目標在眼前 超大型巨人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.95,0:00:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這是個機會
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.28,0:00:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}絕對不要放過
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.76,0:00:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}唷!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.07,0:00:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}五年沒見了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.17,0:02:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這傢伙...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.57,0:02:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}居然以固定砲為目標
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.82,0:02:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}看來針對開關門也不是偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.61,0:03:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}果然這傢伙有...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.73,0:03:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}智慧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.29,0:03:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但是這是個機會
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.93,0:03:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}能破壞城牆的只有他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.37,0:03:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}只要能夠收拾掉他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.86,0:03:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}太弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.42,0:03:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}到手啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.70,0:03:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}好... 好熱!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.85,0:03:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}上啊!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.20,0:03:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}打偏了?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.17,0:03:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.89,0:04:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}超大型巨人消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.46,0:04:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連 是你打敗的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.42,0:04:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不對
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.40,0:04:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}跟五年前一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.40,0:04:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那傢伙突然出現
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.24,0:04:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}又突然消失掉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.84,0:04:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.78,0:04:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我讓他跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.87,0:04:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你在抱歉什麼 我們根本無法動彈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.79,0:04:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}喂 是說這個的時候嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.42,0:04:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}城牆已經被破壞掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.34,0:04:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不快點補起來的話 巨人可又要進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.87,0:04:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你們在幹嘛?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.39,0:04:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}超大型巨人出現 即視同作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.23,0:04:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}立刻回到本部
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.97,0:04:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}有和他接觸過的 記得向本部回報
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.76,0:04:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.47,0:04:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}期待先遣部隊的好表現
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.30,0:05:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}請將帶走的財物縮小在最小範圍內
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.50,0:05:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}冷靜地前往避難
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.46,0:05:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這裡被突破的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.29,0:05:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}五年前的慘劇又將再次上演
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.35,0:05:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我們要在這裡阻止巨人們前進
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.86,0:05:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}迎擊準備
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.76,0:05:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}開砲!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.56,0:05:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}上啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.56,0:05:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你們這些訓練兵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.29,0:05:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}也是通過了畢業演習的優秀士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.49,0:05:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}期待你們在這次作戰中的表現
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.01,0:05:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}沒事的 漢娜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.38,0:05:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我一定會保護妳的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.42,0:05:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}法蘭茲...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.26,0:05:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}沒事吧 阿爾敏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.61,0:05:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.86,0:06:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這毛病很快就會停止
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.59,0:06:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但是 現在情況不太妙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.28,0:06:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就現況而言 我們沒有將8公尺寬的大洞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.86,0:06:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}馬上填補起來的技術
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.41,0:06:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}前門附近的那塊岩石也是 到最後還是無法搬回去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.74,0:06:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}在無法修補大洞的這點上 這座城市將會被遺棄
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.97,0:06:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}羅塞之牆被突破
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.06,0:06:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}也只是時間上的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.37,0:06:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}況且只要他們有心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.64,0:06:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}無論何時都能夠將人類趕盡殺絕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.30,0:06:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}阿爾敏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.05,0:06:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}冷靜點!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.50,0:06:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}現在和當時不同
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.23,0:06:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}人類已經不會...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.71,0:06:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}再輸給巨人了!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.18,0:06:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}抱歉...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.30,0:06:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.24,0:07:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}喂 你有在認真下嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.55,0:07:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你看 又是我贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.09,0:07:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}明明每個月都跟我下一次
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.94,0:07:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你還是沒進步呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.41,0:07:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}皮克希斯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.76,0:07:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不 不
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.03,0:07:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我還不夠格贏巴爾托公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.51,0:07:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你不是負責南方司令的最高權力者嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.51,0:07:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}以這種程度的技術跟頭腦 是想要怎樣贏巨人呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.08,0:07:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}皮克希斯司令
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.85,0:07:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}有傳令
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.37,0:07:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你想幹嘛? 無禮的...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.27,0:07:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}托洛斯特區出現了超大型巨人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.35,0:07:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}開關門被破壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.22,0:08:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這真是好喝的酒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.82,0:08:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}作為戰場上的朋友 我就虛心收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.17,0:08:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.57,0:08:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}等等 皮克希斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.77,0:08:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}皮克希斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.07,0:08:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}給我等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.81,0:08:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我可不允許你離開這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.97,0:08:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}立刻給我召集士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.93,0:08:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}保衛我的領地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.09,0:08:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這才是你的職務吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.36,0:08:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}巴爾托公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.96,0:08:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}現在托洛斯特區的士兵們可是拼上性命在戰鬥唷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.95,0:08:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}司令 我去準備馬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.29,0:08:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}然後我想恐怕會有很多人失去性命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.42,0:08:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}而現在我在說話的這一刻也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.40,0:08:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}反正也是些廉價的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.14,0:08:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}捨棄掉就好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.04,0:09:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}況且在棋盤上一直輸給我的你 去了狀況也不會有所改變
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.23,0:09:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}請您安心 公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.01,0:09:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}在實戰上面對巨人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.65,0:09:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}沒有司令親自出手的必要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.31,0:09:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}別說了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.87,0:09:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}巴爾托公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.50,0:09:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就請您一如往常地度過安穩的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.87,0:09:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}喂...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.13,0:09:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}皮克希斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.58,0:09:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}給我回來 皮克希斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.41,0:09:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}皮克希斯!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.13,0:09:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那麼就照平時訓練一樣分成各班
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.81,0:09:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}在駐紮軍團的指揮下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.01,0:09:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}進行補給支援 情報傳遞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.26,0:09:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}以及討伐巨人等任務
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.35,0:10:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}前衛部由駐紮軍團負責
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.36,0:10:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}中衛部由我們率領的訓練兵團負責
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.40,0:10:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}而後衛部則以駐紮軍團的精銳部隊負責
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.40,0:10:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}依照報告前衛部已經全滅了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.54,0:10:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}外圍的那群廢物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.15,0:10:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}允許了巨人的進攻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.73,0:10:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.82,0:10:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}現在處於的狀況 就算後門遭盔甲巨人破壞也不足為奇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.53,0:10:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}怎麼會...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.62,0:10:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}騙人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.32,0:10:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}羅塞之牆也被破壞掉的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.95,0:10:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}正式聽令
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.05,0:10:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}現在是前衛部的迎擊期
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.93,0:10:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這次作戰的目的只有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.35,0:10:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}在居民避難完成以前死守羅塞之牆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.53,0:10:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}然後 我想你們知道的 陣前逃亡將處以死刑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.74,0:10:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}大家準備好獻上自己的心臟!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.22,0:10:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}解散!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.48,0:10:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.15,0:11:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為什麼是今天...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.30,0:11:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}明明我明天就能夠到內地去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.37,0:11:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}沒事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.35,0:11:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不要... 不要... 不要... 不要...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.42,0:11:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}礙眼!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.15,0:11:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}喂 約翰...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.39,0:11:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.37,0:11:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你說我怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.08,0:11:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}別給我說得這麼悠哉 你這趕著去投胎的傢伙!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.48,0:11:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你是因為自願進入調查軍團 所以早已有送死的覺悟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.89,0:11:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我可是明天開始就要去內地的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.21,0:11:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}冷靜點!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.01,0:11:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}冷靜點等死是嗎!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.99,0:11:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不對 你給我想起來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.08,0:11:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我們在訓練兵團的這三年
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.21,0:11:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這三年我們有好幾次都差點死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.91,0:11:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}也有真的死掉的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.06,0:12:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}退出的人跟被趕走的人也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.38,0:12:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但是我們活了下來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.47,0:12:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}沒錯吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.91,0:12:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就算是今天我們也能夠活下去!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.32,0:12:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}今天活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.41,0:12:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}明天不就能去內地了?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.70,0:12:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}該死的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.78,0:12:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}走啦 達茲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.55,0:12:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不要給我一直哭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.39,0:12:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.42,0:12:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}一旦戰鬥陷入混亂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.07,0:12:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你就來我身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.42,0:12:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}蛤?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.52,0:12:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我跟妳是不同小組的吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.90,0:12:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}在混亂之下 就無法如想像般地順利
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.38,0:12:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}由我來保護你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.94,0:12:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你在說什...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.13,0:12:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}阿卡曼訓練兵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.45,0:12:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}特別准許妳隸屬後衛部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.53,0:12:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}給我跟上來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.41,0:12:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}等... 以我的程度只會拖累大家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.51,0:12:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我不是在問妳的判斷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.41,0:12:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}如今才避難已經晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.26,0:12:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}居民的附近需要更多的精銳保護
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.37,0:13:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.33,0:13:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}喂!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.10,0:13:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}給我適可而止一點 米卡莎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.33,0:13:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不要連妳都給我亂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.85,0:13:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}現在可是人類滅亡的危機
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.14,0:13:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}妳在那邊堅持自己的判斷是怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.25,0:13:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.84,0:13:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我不夠冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.10,0:13:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我只有一個請求
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.87,0:13:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}請你不要死
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.35,0:13:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我不會死的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.89,0:13:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我怎麼可以...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.78,0:13:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}在這邊就死掉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.71,0:13:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}因為我還不了解這個世界的真實姿態
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.46,0:13:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}遺留下來的歷史文獻裡並沒有紀錄巨人出現的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.97,0:14:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}幾乎是完全不明的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.75,0:14:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}現在已經清楚的巨人生態
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.10,0:14:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是來自於調查軍團的最新報告書
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.09,0:14:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}無法確認巨人具備像人類般的智慧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.13,0:14:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}因此不曾有過跟我們溝通的例子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.80,0:14:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}巨人身體的構造跟其他生物有著根本上的不同
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.89,0:14:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}完全沒有生殖器官
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.66,0:14:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}繁殖方式也是不明
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.34,0:14:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但幾乎都是男性的體格
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.79,0:14:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}他們的身體具有極高的溫度
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.66,0:14:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}而且最難以理解的是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.11,0:14:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}對人類以外的生物完全不感興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.07,0:14:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}巨人唯一行動原理就是吃人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.95,0:14:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但從巨人能在無人類的環境下存活百年以上這點來想
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.46,0:14:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}能夠推測出進食這點並非必要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.48,0:14:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.58,0:14:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}目的不在於捕食
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.64,0:15:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}而是進行殺戮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.76,0:15:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}然後
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.70,0:15:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}將人類逼到如此絕境的最大原因是...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.62,0:15:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}巨人令人驚訝的生命力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.42,0:15:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}以前的人類雖然擁有大砲技術
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.85,0:15:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不過光是這樣 還是無法與之抗衡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.85,0:15:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}巨人即使頭被打飛也不會死
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.10,0:15:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}雖然個體會有差異
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.19,0:15:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但是失去的頭部會在一到兩分鐘內恢復原狀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.98,0:15:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}怎麼會...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.37,0:15:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}明明光是大隻就很難應付了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.41,0:15:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}教官 那麼巨人是不死之身嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.89,0:15:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}並不是不死之身
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.93,0:15:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}打倒巨人的方法只有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.12,0:15:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}朝這裡下手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.35,0:15:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}巨人一旦這個部位受到嚴重的損傷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.27,0:15:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就會因無法再生而死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.43,0:15:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}因此為了切下較硬的肉塊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.49,0:15:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就要使用這兩把刀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.27,0:15:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}只要攻擊能夠擊中巨人的要害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.44,0:16:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就能夠在不令其再生的情況下即刻死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.69,0:16:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我說 阿爾敏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.56,0:16:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你不覺得這是個好機會嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.17,0:16:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}在進入調查軍團之前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.88,0:16:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}如果能在首場戰役有所表現
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.08,0:16:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}身為新兵的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.83,0:16:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}勢必能夠快速晉升
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.05,0:16:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是啊... 沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.93,0:16:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我先告訴你們兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.55,0:16:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這次自願加入調查軍團的人可多了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.02,0:16:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}剛才雖然被艾連搶先一步
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.60,0:16:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不過這次我可不會輸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.04,0:16:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你說的唷 托瑪斯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.04,0:16:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}來比比看誰可以獵到最多隻巨人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.22,0:16:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你可別在數量上作弊喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.61,0:16:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}第三十四班 推進!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.49,0:16:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}前去支援前衛部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.45,0:16:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}好!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.20,0:16:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}走吧!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.04,0:16:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}喔!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.22,0:17:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}已經有那麼多巨人...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.29,0:17:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}前衛部隊根本全滅了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.80,0:17:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}在搞三小啊 那些平時作威作福的前輩們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.88,0:17:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}絕對不是我太過樂觀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.73,0:17:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這實在是...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.37,0:17:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是奇行種!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.31,0:17:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}快閃開!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.69,0:17:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}奇怪...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.66,0:18:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你在幹什麼!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.06,0:18:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.84,0:18:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}住手 別單獨行動!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.05,0:18:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}給我站住!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.95,0:18:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你竟敢把托瑪斯...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.24,0:18:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我絕對...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.81,0:18:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}絕對不會讓你逃走!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.66,0:18:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.17,0:18:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.74,0:19:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}住手... 住手啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.31,0:19:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為什麼... 我...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.64,0:19:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}會這樣看著夥伴們被吃掉的景象...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.69,0:19:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為什麼... 我的身體...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.25,0:19:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}會無法動彈呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.35,0:19:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}阿... 阿爾敏...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.12,0:19:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.70,0:19:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.32,0:19:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.25,0:19:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}怎麼了? 阿爾敏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.75,0:20:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這本書是爺爺偷藏起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.10,0:20:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是描寫外面世界的書
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.55,0:20:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你說是描寫外面世界的書?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.10,0:20:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那不是違禁品嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.75,0:20:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}小心被憲兵團抓走喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.21,0:20:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}現在不是說這個的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.09,0:20:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}根據這本書上的記載
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.36,0:20:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這個世界上大半都被名為「大海」的水所包圍著呢!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.43,0:20:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}而且「大海」全部都是鹽水
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.21,0:20:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你是說鹽?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.84,0:20:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你騙肖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.00,0:20:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}鹽不是很貴重嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.24,0:20:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}商人一定馬上就會搶光了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.81,0:20:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}「大海」寬廣到取之不盡用之不竭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.64,0:20:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}怎麼可...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.88,0:20:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不只是鹽堆得像座山
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.59,0:20:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}火焰的水
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.98,0:20:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}結冰的大地
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.32,0:20:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}砂的冰原
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.11,0:20:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}外面的世界一定比這牆內寬廣好幾倍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.07,0:20:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}外面的世界...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.52,0:20:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}然後 這雖然還是秘密...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.97,0:20:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我爸爸跟媽媽說這次要去外面的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.05,0:21:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}外面的世界啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.42,0:21:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}欸 艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.35,0:21:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}如果哪天我們可以到外面的世界探險就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.04,0:21:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.45,0:21:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我怎麼可以..死在這裡...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.99,0:21:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}阿爾敏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.50,0:21:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是你...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.02,0:21:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}告訴我的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.03,0:21:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}所以我才...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.09,0:21:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}想到外面的...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.83,0:21:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}世界去...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.12,0:21:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連! 快...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.76,0:23:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}突然下起的雨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.07,0:23:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那安靜的雨聲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.16,0:23:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}潮濕的空氣
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.58,0:24:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}微弱的雨之甜味
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.09,0:24:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}讓米卡莎想起過去那悽慘的事件
